{"tid":1809734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"武漢不明原因肺炎個案增至44宗　重症11宗","createTime":"2020-01-03T10:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T10:17:33.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d04c883dab72ae6f86f4a1e009cc58172727230e","tid":1809734,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"武漢不明原因肺炎個案至今增至44宗，其中重症有11宗，其餘患者情況穩定，所有患者都在當地醫院接受隔離治療，目前未發現明顯人傳人證據，亦未有醫護人員感染。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市衛健委通報，流行病學調查顯示，部分病例來自當地華南海鮮城經營戶，主要病徵是發燒，少數人呼吸困難，當局的病原鑒定和病因溯源工作，已經排除流感、禽流感、腺病毒感染等常見呼吸道疾病。<br />\n<br />\n當局對121名密切接觸者進行醫學觀察，並繼續追蹤其他接觸者。國家和省衛生健康委高度重視，派出工作組和專家組到武漢指導應對疫情工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500870-20200103.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500870-20200103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7P3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=9c2a084f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500870-20200103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4a9b9c40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500870-20200103.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"aadabdfc918f836a61645af4ebe08db55a50dafb","tid":1809734,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f8d81bc39ee2cea3319959e7dbd2a5e873e59e","tid":1809734,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.g